snippet.title: Abysm 2: Spirit Falcon [1] Raiding Estates
snippet.description:
This is public beta v1 for Spirit Falcon, so any issues here will likely be ironed out in later releases.

You can get it here: https://www.doomworld.com/forum/topic/126711-abysm-2-expansion-spirit-falcon-public-beta-v1/

It's been a few months since I played the last expansion, but it didn't take long to come back to me. I'm still in the pea shooting phase, although I might just be being too stingy with my ammo at the moment.

Having a good time, although I have no idea what it was that I picked up at the end of the Spirit Temple. I assume it was some sort of boon.
